sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/ODH Dashboard
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as KubeRay Operator<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant HeadPod as Ray Head Pod<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    participant WorkerPods as Ray Worker Pods<br/>6379/TCP Redis
    participant Autoscaler as Autoscaler Sidecar
    participant ExternalRedis as External Redis<br/>6379/TCP (Optional)

    Note over User,ExternalRedis: Flow 1: RayCluster Creation

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Head Pod<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Services<br/>6379, 8265, 10001, 8000/TCP
    K8sAPI-->>HeadPod: Start Ray Head<br/>GCS + Dashboard
    K8sAPI-->>WorkerPods: Start Ray Workers
    WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Register with GCS<br/>6379/TCP Redis Protocol

    opt GCS Fault Tolerance Enabled
        HeadPod->>ExternalRedis: Persist GCS State<br/>6379/TCP, Password Auth
    end

    Note over User,ExternalRedis: Flow 2: RayJob Submission

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayJob CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster (if needed)<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>HeadPod: Submit Job via Dashboard<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute Tasks<br/>6379/TCP GCS
    WorkerPods->>HeadPod: Return Results
    Operator->>HeadPod: Poll Job Status<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    HeadPod-->>Operator: Job Complete
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update RayJob Status<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,ExternalRedis: Flow 3: RayService Inference

    User->>K8sAPI: Create RayService CR<br/>Auth: User Credentials
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create RayCluster<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>HeadPod: Deploy Serve Application<br/>8265/TCP HTTP
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Ingress/Route<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    User->>HeadPod: POST /predictions<br/>8000/TCP HTTP<br/>Optional Auth
    HeadPod->>WorkerPods: Distribute Inference<br/>Internal
    WorkerPods-->>HeadPod: Predictions
    HeadPod-->>User: JSON Response

    Note over User,ExternalRedis: Flow 4: Autoscaling

    Autoscaler->>HeadPod: Query GCS Metrics<br/>6379/TCP Redis
    HeadPod-->>Autoscaler: Resource Utilization
    Autoscaler->>K8sAPI: Scale Worker Replicas<br/>443/TCP HTTPS<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI->>Operator: Reconcile Event<br/>Watch Trigger
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Update Worker Pods<br/>ServiceAccount Token
